avg_query.query: Aggregate Average Example Query - AVG QUERY
avg_query.sparql: PREFIX qpr: <http://istresearch.com/qpr> SELECT (AVG(?weight) AS ?avg_weight)  WHERE {   ?cluster a qpr:cluster ;     qpr:seed '9164027085' ;     qpr:weight ?weight ;     qpr:ad ?ad . }
